{"tid":1873481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《上流寄生族》導演奉俊昊年青時為理想上街　因抗爭擲汽油彈被捕","createTime":"2020-02-10T16:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T15:15:14.000Z","uid":112551,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08f954852571f5a041a1c07727dcf210f28c19de","tid":1873481,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wc7aonL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWc7aonL.png&h=e2482f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講起2020年的「第92屆奧斯卡金像獎」，最令人驚喜的莫過於是韓國電影《上流寄生族》勇奪最佳影片、最佳原創劇本，以及最佳國際影片4個獎項，其中《上流寄生族》的導演奉俊昊更榮獲最佳導演一獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3984386/org/ab2b27b31cfec5093b0ba1cce4a4b0f8.jpg/AMoedvmQUUjVVR5ex15IdFPaJuS03LiQSPTcmUj03Jk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3984386%2Forg%2Fab2b27b31cfec5093b0ba1cce4a4b0f8.jpg%2FAMoedvmQUUjVVR5ex15IdFPaJuS03LiQSPTcmUj03Jk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a0591c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奉俊昊憑《上流寄生族》奪得最佳導演獎。（網上擷圖）<br />\n<br />\n其實這位韓國導演奉俊昊，並不是一開始就走上電影的道路。在他的大學時期，韓國面臨「光州事件」、「六月民主運動」等各種示威浪潮。當時就讀於延世大學社會學系的他，雖然出身於中產家庭，但青年時的他也與其他學生一樣，懷着滿腔理想上街抗議，更曾因熱血丟擲汽油彈被逮補。有統計指，當時的示威規模之大，幾乎每名延世大學的學生都最少參加過一次抗議。<br />\n<br />\n在1990年，他更參與了韓國電影界的「光頭運動」，最後亦成為捍衛了韓國本土電影配額，而他勇於表達的性格，拍攝眾多社會階層陰暗面的電影，也間接令他被前總統朴槿惠政府列於「藝文界黑名單」上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzhxBHR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzhxBHR.png&h=17e95f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSBB3nX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSBB3nX.jpg&h=7a3195b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"733ab3f1db1c966b50fc955718e4720dd6467d11","tid":1873481,"uid":3553,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"韓流怪客，殺人回憶，母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺人回憶真係睇左好多次<br />\n無諗過上年竟然搵到真兇"},{"pid":"7c0adb56ee9acafa70691d19a35c994846a5a11b","tid":1873481,"uid":88491,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"733ab3f1db1c966b50fc955718e4720dd6467d11","tid":1873481,"uid":3553,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"韓流怪客，殺人回憶，母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺人回憶真係睇左好多次<br />\n無諗過上年竟然搵到真兇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"殺人回憶最後個幕宋康昊望住鏡頭好深刻，好彩終於搵到兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋韓流怪客都算係我第一套睇既韓國片"},{"pid":"ffb4ac6ad6c088c5e1ec746df1cb365d93181139","tid":1873481,"uid":86236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069405029e42f49fce10c06a16d90d476edf171f","tid":1873481,"uid":12558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"火魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff837d278e3a7897b48268cc073c483bc996b7b2","tid":1873481,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6127447239959a6962f2ebee24d3d6d2262961b9","tid":1873481,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}